{"tid":94351,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"加國出生兒子申特區護照被拒 律師司法覆核敗訴兼付訟費","createTime":"2017-01-25T07:06:06.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-25T12:43:57.000Z","uid":33028,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6a45902fb69a425d1ad406e50b46d3d275249720","tid":94351,"uid":33028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T07:06:06.000Z","msg":"擁有加拿大籍的律師夫婦2003年為避沙士疫情到加拿大短暫生活，長子同年在加國出生後舉家回港，他們先後獲香港永久居民身份，但長子申請特區護照卻遭入境處拒絕，任職律師的父親勞亨順為此代子申請司法覆核，法庭今下判詞判其敗訴，指其子雖有中國血統及為香港居民，惟他並非在中國或香港出生，父母也非中國國籍，故並不符《中國國籍法》的要求，不算香港中國同胞。<br />\n<br />\n勞亨順曾以人大常委就《中國國籍法》內容釋法，認為自己是中國同胞故為中國公民，但法庭認為申請人誤解當中意義，並指有關解釋是因應香港97回歸的歷史背景，為持有英國屬土公民護照（BDTC）或英國國民（海外）護照（BNO）的人士說明處理的方法，並非就中國香港同胞作定義。<br />\n法官又同意入境處的說法，指申請人只要歸化中國，便可獲得特區護照，但這並非法庭需要決定的事項。法庭最後判勞敗訴，兼要付入境處85%訟費。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20170125/56221068\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20170125%2F56221068&d=QRiv9YnaLWrwMBsY1jL0JZkBtgkcD0hE3Em2wkgk6m8%3D&h=b26ac7d2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20170125%2F56221068&h=4fe33efe\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20170125/56221068</a>"},{"pid":"77fec84f194381c4482184871304cc0ee0afa962","tid":94351,"uid":54181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T07:07:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3c6d07d6b461339caf4362a11e7c172600bc21c5","tid":94351,"uid":17103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T11:22:51.000Z","msg":"傻仔你賣書咪直刻香港變中籍囉付送埋洗頭艇添."},{"pid":"329de4af35e2894ee4d26e657016672540384acb","tid":94351,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T11:42:41.000Z","msg":"咩叫中國血統？！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b71982ecb1a52eb7767ae463039ae722c7815d6a","tid":94351,"uid":57237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T12:41:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4127d9179e30d9a687886e1d2c73813412a731b6","tid":94351,"uid":41245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T12:43:25.000Z","msg":"大中華膠真係冇用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"102faf70f6787d2607c8a5d7597a29873c730a3b","tid":94351,"uid":46454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T12:43:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>識玩，兩本護照進可攻，退可守</blockquote><br />\n雙重國籍只會越黎越唔抵玩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n稅務資料交換呀 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}